title: Barbara Kruger Clutch
description:
Clutch developed from Barbara Kruger’s (Untitled) Money Talks, 2021, from the exhibit THINKING OF YOU. I MEAN ME. I MEAN YOU. at The Art Institute of Chicago.

Combining images with provocative text, Kruger uses direct address—along with humor, vigilance, and empathy—to expose and undermine the power dynamics of identity, desire, and consumerism.

  • Dimensions: 5 x 8 in.
  • Material: Embossed Full Grain Leather.
  • Zipper closure and wrist strap.
